<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="possibly-adv">possibly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pɒsəbli/    美 /'pɑːsəbli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-maybe-perhaps">1.★ <strong>可能；也许(maybe / perhaps)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He could possibly be the most beautiful baby I’d ever seen. 
他可能是我见过的最漂亮的婴儿。</p><footer>2008 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>无论如何；竟然：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>can’t possibly</strong> accept your advice. 
无论如何我都不能接受你的建议。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How can you possibly miss the news? It has been on TV all day long. 
你怎么会没看到这条新闻？电视上一整天都在播呢。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>尽可能：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ll call you back as soon as I possibly can. 
我会尽早给你回电话。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="could-you-possibly">could you possibly</h3>
<p>1.<strong>... [表示郑重的请求] 您能…吗：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Could you possibly ask her to bring along that book?
您能让她把那本书带来吗？</p><footer>2008 天津</footer></div></div>